<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Test Available: {{testTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .test-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .test-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .test-details {
            display: grid;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            width: 120px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        
        .due-date {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .due-date p {
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .test-info {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .test-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                width: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìã New Test Available</h1>
            <p>You have been assigned a new test</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello{{#if recipientName}} {{recipientName}}{{/if}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                {{#if instructorName}}{{instructorName}}{{else}}Your instructor{{/if}} has assigned you a new test. Please review the details below and complete it by the due date.
            </div>
            
            <div class="test-info">
                <div class="test-title">{{testTitle}}</div>
                
                <div class="test-details">
                    {{#if testDescription}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Description:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{testDescription}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Due Date:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{formatDate dueDate 'long'}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    {{#if duration}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Duration:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{duration}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if instructorName}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Instructor:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{instructorName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="due-date">
                <p>‚è∞ Due: {{formatDate dueDate 'long'}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{testUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Test</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Important Reminders:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Make sure you have a stable internet connection</li>
                    <li>Complete the test in one session if possible</li>
                    <li>Submit your answers before the due date</li>
                    <li>Contact support if you experience any technical issues</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Good luck with your test! We're here to support your learning journey.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>
                {{companyName}} | 
                {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>{{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 